Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: seantis.dir.eventsportlet
Version: 1.0rc1
Summary: Portlet for displaying events.
Home-page: https://github.com/seantis/seantis.dir.eventsportlet
Author: Seantis GmbH
Author-email: info@seantis.ch
License: GPL
Description: 
        
        seantis.dir.eventsportlet shows events coming from a seantis.dir.events.
        
        
        Dependencies
        ------------
        
        seantis.dir.eventsportlet relies on Plone 4.3+ with dexterity.
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        1. Use Plone 4.3 or newer
        
        ::
        
            extends =
                http://dist.plone.org/release/4.3/versions.cfg
        
        2. Add the module to your instance eggs
        
        ::
        
            [instance]
            eggs +=
                seantis.dir.eventsportlet
        
        
        3. Ensure that the i18n files are compiled by adding
        
        ::
        
            [instance]
            ...
            environment-vars = 
                ...
                zope_i18n_compile_mo_files true
        
        
        4. Install dexterity and seantis.dir.eventsportlet using portal_quickinstaller
        
        
